cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with communication systems and optimization of transmission delays subject to energy constraints. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves energy harvesting, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of optimization techniques and policies suggests that it could also belong to cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
